WEBVTT

00:02:31.080 --> 00:02:32.736
Child soldiers,

00:02:32.760 --> 00:02:35.056
children as young as my nephews

00:02:35.080 --> 00:02:39.216
being abducted,
given AK-47s and forced to kill,

00:02:39.240 --> 00:02:42.296
not just anyone, but oftentimes
forced to kill their own parents,

00:02:42.320 --> 00:02:44.096
their own siblings --

00:02:44.120 --> 00:02:48.736
a rebel army committing mass murder
for no political or religious reason,

00:02:48.760 --> 00:02:49.960
just because.

00:02:50.880 --> 00:02:52.400
25 years.

00:02:53.080 --> 00:02:55.896
25 years this conflict has been going on.

00:02:55.920 --> 00:02:57.336
I'm 20 years old,

00:02:57.360 --> 00:02:59.840
so that makes this conflict
five years older than me.